Package uk.co.westhawk.snmp.beans

Contains SNMPv1 beans.

See:
          Description

Class Summary
AnnexModemStatusBean This bean is written for Remote Annex 2000 access server.
AscendActiveSessionBean This bean is written for the Ascend Router from Lucent Technologies, Inc.
DialogChannelStatusBean This bean is written for a Dialogic card.
InterfaceIndexesBean This bean collects information about the number of interfaces on a system and their index.
IsHostReachableBean This bean will determine whether the host+port is up, by sending an UpSincePdu.
NcdPerfDataBean This bean collects information about a IBM Network Computer.
NTPrintQBean This bean collects the names of the print queues installed on a NT server.
NTServiceNamesBean This bean collects the names of the network services installed on a NT server.
NTSharedResBean This bean collects the names of the shared resources installed on a NT server.
NTUserNamesBean This bean collects the names of the network users installed on a NT server.
OneInterfaceBean This bean collects information about one interface.
OneNTPrintQBean This bean collects information about one NT print queue installed on a NT server.
OneNTServiceBean This bean collects information about one NT network service installed on a NT server.
OneNTSharedResBean This bean collects information about one NT shared resource installed on a NT server.
SNMPBean This bean forms the base of the SNMP beans.
SNMPRunBean This bean forms the base of the Runnable SNMP beans.
UsmBeingDiscoveredBean This bean handles being discovered as an authoritative engine by an non-authoritative engine (SNMPv3 only).
UsmDiscoveryBean This bean performs the SNMPv3 USM discovery process.
